===========================
Grilo Plugin for Rhythmbox
===========================


How to install it
==================

Copy the *grilo-plugin* folder to ~/.gnome2/rhythmbox/plugins .

Run Rhythmbox and enable **Grilo Plugin** from the *Edit > Plugins* menu.


How to use it
==============

Choose **Grilo Plugin** from the left part in Rhythmbox; a list of services 
should be already present.

Double click a folder to retrieve its items, if an item is not a folder, and 
double click it to add it to the play list.

